 "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_large.png?m=1715439154", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_xlarge.png?m=1715439154", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_xlarge.png?m=1715439154", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/796c/341e/663698_xlarge.png?m=1715439154", "created": 1700591445, "last_modified": 1715439154}, "last_reply_by": "klarkzh", "last_touched": 1716145315, "title": "买苹果产品，建议抢首发", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1042069", "created": 1716120834, "deleted": 0, "content": "往往首发的产品都装载内部系统，比如 iphone15 ，搭载 ios17.0 （ 21A326 、21A327)这个固件在网上是下载不到的，https://ipsw.me/iPhone15,4 ，属于工厂预装（ Preinstalled ），只有代工厂能拿到。这个版本是专为新款手机打造的，经过研发过程长时间测试，发热和续航都很不错，后期升级是给所有型号的手机，不会为某一个型号单独优化。", "content_rendered": "<p>往往首发的产品都装载内部系统，比如 iphone15 ，搭载 ios17.0 （ 21A326 、21A327)这个固件在网上是下载不到的，<a href=\"https://ipsw.me/iPhone15,4\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://ipsw.me/iPhone15,4</a> ，属于工厂预装（ Preinstalled ），只有代工厂能拿到。这个版本是专为新款手机打造的，经过研发过程长时间测试，发热和续航都很不错，后期升级是给所有型号的手机，不会为某一个型号单独优化。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1716120834, "replies": 53, "id": 1042069}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 62780, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8966, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 359662, "username": "basncy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/basncy", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d933cc2cac223cdf7b8aa0ada634874d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d933cc2cac223cdf7b8aa0ada634874d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d933cc2cac223cdf7b8aa0ada634874d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1540884171, "last_modified": 1700908237}, "last_reply_by": "philsilver", "last_touched": 1716147993, "title": "劝大家不要用微软的邮箱, 会丢信且无提示.", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1042033", "created": 1716107346, "deleted": 0, "content": "它家有 IP 黑名单(关键字: S3140), 直接把某些小厂的邮件丢了, 连垃圾箱都不会进.\r\n现象是, 发件人点击发送后, 然后就没有然后了. 这封信不仅收件人的邮箱(包括垃圾箱)找不到, 连发件人这边有可观的概率没有退信提示(显示已发送).\r\n\r\n好处是垃圾箱清静, 坏处是收件箱也清静, 结果是可用性 80%.\r\n\r\nhttps://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook_com/forum/all/hotmailoutlook-block-list-s3140-blocks-all-new/699f3a56-406e-4804-97e2-cbe23b9bb01c", "content_rendered": "它家有 IP 黑名单(关键字: S3140), 直接把某些小厂的邮件丢了, 连垃圾箱都不会进.<br />现象是, 发件人点击发送后, 然后就没有然后了. 这封信不仅收件人的邮箱(包括垃圾箱)找不到, 连发件人这边有可观的概率没有退信提示(显示已发送).<br /><br />好处是垃圾箱清静, 坏处是收件箱也清静, 结果是可用性 80%.<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook_com/forum/all/hotmailoutlook-block-list-s3140-blocks-all-new/699f3a56-406e-4804-97e2-cbe23b9bb01c\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook_com/forum/all/hotmailoutlook-block-list-s3140-blocks-all-new/699f3a56-406e-4804-97e2-cbe23b9bb01c</a>", "last_modified": 1716107346, "replies": 45, "id": 1042033}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 11466, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5815, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 253267, "username": "RickyLin7", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/RickyLin7", "websi